pitch:
Hi there!
My name is Gerald, I am a Software Engineer for Optum in Spencer Dock and I am currently looking for accommodation for one in Dublin.
This room caught my eye this morning, I am interested in renting it. 
Here is a little about me: 
- 25 years old
- Irish National
- I can provide proof of employment upon request
- I can provide references upon request
- Not paying through any housing schemes.
- No pets, non-smoker
- Tidy & Sociable
I'll be down in Dublin this weekend and could view the room and move in right away, as long as that suits you of course!
Please let me know if there is anything I can provide for you. Here is my number if you would like to chat! _
Kindest Regards, 
Gerald Wogan
